wikipedia_page.main: James Dunn (25 November 1923 – 31 December 2014) was a Scottish footballer, who spent the majority of his league career with Wolverhampton Wanderers. He was the son of a Scottish international footballer, also named Jimmy Dunn.

response: James, Jim or Jimmy Dunn may refer to:

*Jimmy Dunn (comedian), American stand-up comedian and actor
